# Successful political training day

Author: carga

Time: 2023-03-01T71:00:00-04:00

Head Description: 

Description: The day was held on Wednesday 22 from 9 a.m. to 1 p.m., at the headquarters

Images: ['[Chubut-jornada-capacitación-política.jpg](https://pcr.org.ar/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Chubut-jornada-capacitación-política.jpg)']

Type: article

<!--METADATA-->

![](Images/Partido Communista Revolucionario/2023-03-01T71-00-00-04-00/Chubut-jornada-capacitación-política.jpg)The day was held on Wednesday 22 from 9 a.m. to 1 p.m., at the "Renésalamanca" headquarters of the San Cayetano neighborhood, with the active participation of 80 Companions and colleagues.

We continue the first day, held in December 2022 on the extraordinary legitarian of Chubut.

We first made a tribute to our first general secretary of the PCR, the beloved Comrade Otto Vargas, who died 4 years ago, and around we celebrated the 40 years of our weekly today, our Propagandist and collective organizer, which week a week guides the political action.

Then the plenary was carried out with the reading and analysis of the political time of the demonstration of Wednesday 22. And questions arose, how: who are the "that they carry it in shovel"? What is estate? and others, which were developed with several interventions.

After a snack served by the organizational partners, we went to affirm in two commissions, to analyze the 10 measures of the PTP - PCR. point by point.

There were many questions and opinions about several of the measures: "freezing", "minimum vital and mobile salary", "family basket", "reformamonetaria", "the Leliq" "Vicentin", "the actions of Renova", "Segmented retentions" , "The causes of inflation", "the fishing law", and other issues.

In the development of the course we were commenting together and analyzing the last activities and fighting days of the CCC and the FNC, the persecutions of our leaders and other organizations, the municipal elections Entrelew on April 16, the strengthening of the PTP-PCR and the Front Detodos, the work in the Latin American Community Huerta and the Great Matebingo to be held on April 15. And the organizational work of all compromises and youth.

The colleagues in each circle of readers, working group and commission, will follow the study and collective debate, developing the course with laparitation of all the classmates.

At the end, fellow Fernando García closed the activity and was accompanied by a hot applause. And it was agreed to follow the course with the video on inflation lascauses. We congratulate all the companions who participated, and who were preparing all the halls.

**Correspondent**

