Head Description: Interview with Fernando Almejún, a member of the Liberpueblo organization and a member of the “Mission of International Solidarity and Human Rights” that was in Peru between February 7 and 13.

Description: Companion Almejún tells us that this mission was made “in the face of repeated allegations of human rights violations in the sister Republic and the request for observation and verification, an invitation made by the deputy of together for Peru, Isabel Cortez Aguirre, We decided to carry out this mission that is formed by & Hellip;

