Description: Sol begins by framing the current situation of original women “the oppression of the sisters of the different native peoples of the more than 40 pre -existing nations of the State that are still being developed in our country today, understand that more than 530 years of colonial oppression, We continue with the same state oppression, the overwhelming & Hellip;

