Description: CABA under intense heat, coming from different areas of CABA, Greater Buenos Aires and La Plata, starred in a great day of struggle, in which they claimed: genuine increase in retirement above homelessness, without bonds. Pension moratorium so that thousands can retire. Restitution of the Probienestar Plan. Pami directed by retirees. With & Hellip;

