In the face of growing protest support, today's announcement of the Transportation Franchising and Regulatory Board is announced(LTFRB)that it will dipThe deadline for implementing public utility vehicle(Full)ModernizationProgram. The LTFRB's original plan was beginning June 30, forced to remove the roads traditionally and old jeepneys and UV Express.

