# People's war for freedom and democracy

Author: Philippine Revolution Web Central

Publish Time: 2023-03-01T99:00:00-04:00

Modified Time: 2023-03-01T12:18:18+00:00

Description: Why is there a people in the Philippines? This is because the Filipino people seek to achieve true national independence and democracy for the Motherland.

Images: ['[new-peoples-army-southern-tagalog-1024x512.jpg](https://philippinerevolution.nu/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/new-peoples-army-southern-tagalog-1024x512.jpg)']

